{"tid":247054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(又係強國)少年攝過量咖啡因猝死","createTime":"2017-05-17T13:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T06:51:39.000Z","uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99482d12ca47881e905564bcf5a6ad2085f28cdc","tid":247054,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"少年攝過量咖啡因猝死<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】美國一名16歲健康少年，因在兩小時內喝下大量高咖啡因飲料，導致心律不整死亡。南卡州高中生克里普（Davis Allen Cripe）上月26日在兩小時內喝了麥當勞的牛奶咖啡、大裝Diet Mountain Dew汽水和一罐能量飲品，不久在學校暈倒，其後死亡。驗屍官沃茨（Gary Watts）周一在記者會表示，解剖顯示克里普沒心臟病，體內亦沒發現藥品或酒精。<br />\n<br />\n美國兒科學會建議，12至18歲青少年每天不應攝取超過100毫克咖啡因。歐洲食品安全局2015年指出，攝取逾400毫克的咖啡因可導致心跳加速、血壓增加等問題。克里普估計當時在短時間內喝了約470毫克咖啡因。<br />\n<br />\n（BBC/CNN）"},{"pid":"ed4fbb3294eadbc3aaff4f260bdb2beb0c98aba0","tid":247054,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"台灣都有咖啡因含量標示，仲要規定成人每日勿攝取超過200毫克咖啡因。"},{"pid":"bf275a27dea1146af3a195620c68cb353a929cb8","tid":247054,"uid":66597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:16:18.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"840438bbca13ffa36965e464e52d210807ff270f","tid":247054,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:50:11.000Z","msg":"朝早飲左咖啡<br />\n下就 飲左 red bull<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bf4c4780e7e115abcce9f08ff44fbbd50f42d8","tid":247054,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:52:35.000Z","msg":"試過飲咖啡溝可樂 果晚眼光光"},{"pid":"aaeff97345154673e11cff7f3b4a354817a7bd17","tid":247054,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過飲咖啡溝可樂 果晚眼光光</blockquote><br />\n唔死咪偷笑仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f44af9385eaaf89cc5bddcbe5e2a8534c7b60fd","tid":247054,"uid":82238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":